* Error Handling\nResponsibilities
** Platform Handled
***_ Cluster node failures
***_ Infrastructure-level issues
***_ Auto-recovery
** Engineer's Responsibility
***_ Data-level errors
***_ Application logic failures
** Error Types
*** Invalid Data
****_ Bad formats
****_ Missing required fields
*** Logic Errors
****_ Unexpected values
*** Connection Issues
****_ Timeouts
****_ Service unavailability
** Response Strategies
***_ Terminate pipeline (critical)
***_ Log and continue (non-critical)
@endmindmap
